    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A geophysical technique of surveying involving the measurement of distortions of the earth's normal magnetic field; used in archaeology especially to locate buried remains.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Técnica geofísica de agrimensura que involucra la medida de distorciones del campo magnético normal de la tierra; usado en arqueología especialmente para localizar restos enterrados.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een geofysische onderzoekstechniek waarbij de distorsies van het normale magnetische veld van de aarde worden gemeten; wordt met name gebruikt in de archeologie om begraven overblijfselen te lokaliseren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>地球物理學的測量技術，用來測量常態地磁場的扭曲；考古學上特別應用於定位遭掩埋的遺跡。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
